The userlister macro has a nice feature to show users who are online, if the Login Listener is enabled.

But:
As not everyone might like to be "watched" this way there should be a feature to disable the online status. I. e. a user should be able to specify e. g. in the profile if his/her online status should be shown or not. There should also be a configurable default setting for the creation of new users.

